This is best settings for Imaginator in my opinion.
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/76448/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/76448/?[/url] - preset for vivid weathers

Requires:
IMAGINATOR - Visual Control Device for Skyrim - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13049/

Climates Of Tamriel - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/17802/?
Climates Of Tamriel - Weather Patch - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/39799/?
Realistic Lighting Overhaul - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30450/?
